  "hiringCompany": {
    "uen": "200906486N",
    "description": "<p>GreenTec Energy Pte Ltd (GTE)&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>GreenTec Energy Pte Ltd (GTE) was incorporated in 2009. From a humble start up in handling hazardous oily waste, we progressed, upgraded and extended our environmental services in 2019, having a vision and mission by the board of directors to provide our customers with one stop station services throughout.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our service includes Industrial waste &amp; oily waste.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>To provide a hassle free solution to our customer is always the key approach and to work towards a win-win situation. As a NEA approved environmental company in Singapore, we take all our services seriously and to ensure maximum safety with compliances applied. Every step of our disposal processes are also designed to meet NEA &amp; SCDF requirements, with latest treatment facilities and laboratories to test and treat incoming waste before disposal.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>GTE operates a total land area of about 100,00sqft at 14 Tuas South Street 12 Singapore 696953. With our comprehensive logistics and transportation fleet, we provide prompt and efficient services in transportation of waste to our premises</p>",
